{"tid":2101173,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"首爾市長朴元淳留疑似遺言失蹤　警方搜索未有發現","createTime":"2020-07-09T14:59:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T15:58:16.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5be4372f1923a97957ac4fee5af83ebf6a26973a","tid":2101173,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T14:59:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://stream.881903.com/public/8e09b762630f6284574098a29431272e/2020/07/aa5b7034439e7269b52f0b43ad3a58a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstream.881903.com%2Fpublic%2F8e09b762630f6284574098a29431272e%2F2020%2F07%2Faa5b7034439e7269b52f0b43ad3a58a6.jpg&h=e73d3eb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n南韓首爾市長朴元淳下落不明，警方透過手機定位追蹤到朴元淳在城北洞附近一座山，出動150名警員、無人機及警犬搜索，到目前仍未有發現，警方否認朴元淳已死亡，指搜索行動仍在繼續。 <br />\n<br />\n朴元淳的女兒下午報警，指父親在早上10時許留下懷疑遺言後，離開市長官邸，其後手提電話關閉。<br />\n<br />\n首爾市政府表示，朴元淳因身體不適没有上班，取消全部日程。<br />\n<br />\n南韓傳媒今日報道，首爾市政府一名前職員提出刑事訴訟，指控朴元淳涉嫌利用職權進行性騷擾。<br />\n<br />\n64歲的朴元淳在2011年首次當選首爾市長，去年贏得第3屆任期，他隸屬執政黨共同民主黨，被視為是2022年總統大選的熱門競選人。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2346296\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2346296&d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjo%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=ea45d8d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2346296</a>"},{"pid":"aaa3a0e0736e168339d6c41e59ec78146a87285e","tid":2101173,"uid":132587,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T15:00:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bbb2f245864c9846a62bfbe5d98223b8406a3626","tid":2101173,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T15:01:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ea9269c0c64bad505339c716981eee7555c41f0","tid":2101173,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T15:07:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a7648463e4117455c46dd1acc9efbd7395f440e","tid":2101173,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aaa3a0e0736e168339d6c41e59ec78146a87285e","tid":2101173,"uid":132587,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T15:00:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T15:09:09.000Z","msg":"朴信惠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"014b2fc495f39ffbaa49b998584880251012761f","tid":2101173,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T15:54:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a45e9354fde7fd13ffd59be6a020fa5886041912","tid":2101173,"uid":334953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aaa3a0e0736e168339d6c41e59ec78146a87285e","tid":2101173,"uid":132587,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T15:00:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T15:58:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}